<h4>How World-Class Brands are Winning With Data-Driven Marketing</h4>



<p>Now more than ever, the world’s best brands are relying on data to identify new market opportunities, develop and measure marketing initiatives, and optimize campaigns and content.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Join BrainStation for a discussion with data and marketing industry leaders, as they discuss the leading role data is now playing in marketing, and how brands are optimizing digital spend and marketing performance.&nbsp;<a href="https://brainstation.io/event/online-data-driven-digital-marketing-june2020">Sign Up</a>&nbsp;</p>



